{"tid":2232382,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美中台軍機台海同場較勁  美軍機距香港80公里處來回巡邏","createTime":"2020-10-06T10:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T01:47:48.000Z","uid":337052,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"37dd530d1935084b97240ad73464fb20b38b3298","tid":2232382,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">6天來4次！共機空警500與運8又擾台 美國也出動偵察機繞行我西南海域</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/xTqeiH83FUpfEwNEgsPajgkvFWQ=/760x427/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HRSKXAFKFVHLHFTFJEKMWSGLLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxTqeiH83FUpfEwNEgsPajgkvFWQ%3D%2F760x427%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHRSKXAFKFVHLHFTFJEKMWSGLLU.jpg&h=cec04d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解放軍運8反潛機今又擾台。資料照片<br />\n圖片來源 : 蘋果新聞網<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">台灣西南空域今（6日）出現美國及中共軍機，美軍包括EP-3E電偵機、RC-135W電子偵察機，解放軍則有空警500空中預警機及運8反潛機。</span>空軍雖不願明確證實有上述機型，但強調國軍均運用聯合情監偵，對台灣周邊動態嚴密掌握。至於是否有進入我防空識別區，空軍也會在適當時機公布相關狀況。<br />\n<br />\n時常分享全球各國軍情軍機動態的CANUK78推特平台今指出，美軍一架RC-135W電子偵察機今晨從巴士海峽進入我台灣南部空域後，轉往南海偵搜；而當時也有一架中共解放軍所屬的空警500預警機在我防空識別區西南角外繞飛。<br />\n<br />\n而後CANUK78推特平台也顯示，美軍另一架EP-3E電偵機則從巴士海峽進入後，沿著我防空識別區往中國方向偵搜，但在我防空識別區西南角處則轉往東沙島至巴士海峽繞飛。<br />\n<br />\n另外<span class=\"red\">「台灣西南空域」《臉書》則公布一架疑似共軍運8反潛機則在我防空識別區西南角處，遭我空軍以廣播驅離。根據台灣西南空域所描述的時間，則是近中午左右，而此時應是美軍EP-3E電偵機剛剛經過此空域後，運8反潛機即前來訓練。</span>（王烱華／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201006/IO5TARKGHVBHFNASBNCFTARBEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201006%2FIO5TARKGHVBHFNASBNCFTARBEM%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=bed81925\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2F20201006%2FIO5TARKGHVBHFNASBNCFTARBEM%2F&h=b76dec21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/politics/20201006/IO5TARKGHVBHFNASBNCFTARBEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n台灣西南空域<br />\n <br />\n#台灣西南空域 真熱鬧 補充圖片在留言中<br />\n空域外有一架 #中共軍機 #空警500 #7A42A3 #高度5900公尺 ，空域內有一架 #中共軍機 疑似 #空潛200 #高度3500公尺 ，還有一架 #美國海軍 #P3E #AE1D8A ，領海線上有一架 #漢翔拖靶機<br />\n#台灣西南空域 還有一架 #美國空軍 #RC135偵查機 沿著大陸海岸線80公里左右從汕頭到海南島來回巡邏， #恆春上空 有一架 #國軍 #E2K 盤旋中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120727452_117250240141569_6412041160428110988_o.png?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=vBdlGBjqc38AX-QkIDu&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-4.fna&amp;oh=974f5364feeced9a9ea27ffe9ca132df&amp;oe=5FA29BFC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120727452_117250240141569_6412041160428110988_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DvBdlGBjqc38AX-QkIDu%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-4.fna%26oh%3D974f5364feeced9a9ea27ffe9ca132df%26oe%3D5FA29BFC&h=8a610c40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120646719_117250863474840_561822675504482439_o.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=6JEKwbGWaXQAX-ffPMQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-4.fna&amp;oh=7c0a459f4abbdf113ab23234c22dd7a7&amp;oe=5FA2EA64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120646719_117250863474840_561822675504482439_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D6JEKwbGWaXQAX-ffPMQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-4.fna%26oh%3D7c0a459f4abbdf113ab23234c22dd7a7%26oe%3D5FA2EA64&h=da4aaab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n台灣西南空域<br />\n<br />\n補充還有一架美國空軍RC-135偵查機 62-4134<br />\n沿著大陸海岸線80公里左右從汕頭到海南島來回偵巡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/120703757_117301273469799_7005926736242176172_o.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=dbeb18&amp;_nc_ohc=qL7Lh7hdjwAAX_Weevf&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.ftpe7-4.fna&amp;oh=6293be7228344072e9e68f0f1325e8af&amp;oe=5FA37676\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.ftpe7-4.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F120703757_117301273469799_7005926736242176172_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3Ddbeb18%26_nc_ohc%3DqL7Lh7hdjwAAX_Weevf%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.ftpe7-4.fna%26oh%3D6293be7228344072e9e68f0f1325e8af%26oe%3D5FA37676&h=0565f49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SouthwestAirspaceofTW/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSouthwestAirspaceofTW%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=058ce794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SouthwestAirspaceofTW/</a>"},{"pid":"e61d03c66afa44a7a9a77ee9b432db18137a2a5b","tid":2232382,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"支持美軍保護香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ccde9523d18816bff7f6dc25db272f3415b41e","tid":2232382,"uid":201604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"5分鐘就到香港 仲快過摺被軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf3fcef98a7b7594abb5a1914bb0a9f4d5248d1","tid":2232382,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e61d03c66afa44a7a9a77ee9b432db18137a2a5b","tid":2232382,"uid":304769,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"支持美軍保護香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76672c1b1895c50a443629db8920d4274e